verbose_text: In line with in vitro obtained results that cell stress has a marked influence on early Th17 cell differentiation, the dosing of mice at the start of clinical manifestations of EAE with TUDCA had no effect on disease progression compared with control animals or IL-17 or IFNgamma producing CD4 + T cells in the CNS (XREF_FIG E and XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY D).
